{"id":52294,"title":"[Therapeutic education in adrenal insufficiency: A tool insufficiently used to prevent or treat early acute adrenal insufficiency].","abstract":"Acute adrenal insufficiency is a rare, unknown, and life-threatening emergency. It seems therefore essential to help patients gain or maintain the skills they need to prevent or treat early acute adrenal insufficiency, which is the goal of therapeutic education. A program has been implemented within the service focused on patient empowerment. ","date":"2014-04-15","categories":"Endocrine System Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24613067","annotations":[{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.786341,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Acute (medicine)","weight":0.680879,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Acute_(medicine)"},{"name":"Patient","weight":0.618082,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patient"},{"name":"Education","weight":0.27754,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Education"},{"name":"Emergency","weight":0.214446,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emergency"},{"name":"Adrenal gland","weight":0.106802,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adrenal_gland"},{"name":"Tool","weight":0.0391252,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tool"},{"name":"Adrenal insufficiency","weight":0.0342852,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adrenal_insufficiency"},{"name":"Patient empowerment","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patient_empowerment"},{"name":"Empowerment","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Empowerment"}]}
